          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1696947289307-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sprouts are tender, reduce the heat to medium, add your <strong>cracked black pepper</strong> and <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and cook for a further 1 min or until the sauce has thickened slightly – this is your <strong>Brussels sprouts cacio e pepe sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696947293927-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696947293927-x400.jpg",
