          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696947293927-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>orecchiette</strong> to the sauce with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and give everything a good mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce – this is your<strong> Brussels sprouts cacio e pepe with fresh orecchiette</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
